	<article id="post-155311" class="post-155311 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-consoles category-events category-games tag-microsoft tag-phil-spencer tag-satya-nadella tag-whats-next-for-gaming" data-post-id="155311" data-url="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2021/06/10/whats-next-for-gaming-highlights/" data-next-post="155314" data-next-url="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2021/06/10/satya-nadella-and-phil-spencer-on-gaming-at-microsoft/">

			
